# Workspace Validation Report - 2026-05-28

Status: diagnostic pass only  
Root: `/opt/Axodus`  
Execution mode: no fixes, no production configuration, no live trading, no settlement, no real adapters, no fund movement

## Scope

This pass inspected the Axodus root instructions and the available workspace `.instructions` directories before validation.

`/opt/Axodus` itself is not a Git worktree. The workspace entries are symlinks to `/mnt/d/Rede/Github/Axodus/*`.

